    {
      "timestamp": 1776724097881,
      "source": "manual",
      "category": "build",
      "content": "biome pre-commit hook exits 1 with \"no files processed\" when ALL staged JSON files are in biome's ignore list (progress/data/, items_rules.default.json). Fix: entry in .pre-commit-config.yaml must include --no-errors-on-unmatched. Also: scripts with shebangs need executable bit via `git add --chmod=+x &lt;file&gt;` or pre-commit check-shebang hook blocks commit."
    }
